Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底還能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變那如狹隘庭園般的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相擁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無意識中被刻上的經驗紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當站在懸崖邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦難抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加寬廣的領域\N往更深更大的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著無法預測的世界前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1的反應消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的客人就招待到這兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰結束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha各機返航
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人真的非常努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從戰鬥情況看，他已經不再迷惘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不迷惘的人是不存在的，紫東大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好，有什麼情況嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月，MU也沒什麼動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾有寄到管理部的郵件，\N我就拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣和平的日子能維持下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了，總一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在您要下班了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要外出一天，這段時間裡就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，功刀先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不找個女婿嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是女孩子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要外出，那，什麼…MU…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MU大戰死者聯合悼念大會準備會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，就是這個，真繞口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，你一定要參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是對那些位高權重的人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，對你來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天對你來說是個特別的日子，\N不要太嚴肅了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困好困…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好，你去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有東西忘在仁哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁？仁是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，為什麼她叫你olin？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對女性而言…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物和男人的心，\N得到哪個會比較高興？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道！別問我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠，早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問個問題，女性收到花或禮物之類的會很高興嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然，謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有綾人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑，誰會喜歡那種吃炸蝦沾醬油的男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不是用荷包蛋沾調味汁！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哎，你們這群沒有緊張感的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對MU作戰的最前線就是這樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好，各位！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天司令不在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我代行司令職責一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令不在的時候，不要出什麼差錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令請假，還真是少見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起少見的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才不是遇到久遠了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠妹妹！她怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說忘了拿什麼東西了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一個叫仁的人那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,職員中有這個傢伙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁，仁，仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們說什麼呀？仁不是司令的名字嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀仁，大家都不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人，樹博士說有事找你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好\N各位安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠常常晚上到司令那邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚…晚上！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每週一兩次左右
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每週一兩次？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，他說有一些有趣的東西問我要不要去看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠，能帶綾人去如月博士哪裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上，少佐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，她為什麼總在本部進出呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說久遠，她既不是職員也不是軍人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和綾人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人雖然是平民，\N但他具有操縱RahXephon的奇異能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以認為久遠是以這類方式來協助TERRA的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然每天面對著樂譜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但和我最喜歡的小提琴在一起\N我感到生活很充實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能經常和爸爸見面，有些寂寞…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說下次我演出時您一定會來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時，我有禮物要送給爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一定會開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，一定要來噢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待爸爸能來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的東西就是這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在聽什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月，久遠演奏的小提琴曲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將樂曲錄音後，在發芽階段持續播放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開出了和原始品種有點像又不完全像的花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說一句，那邊的是原始品種
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這邊的花朵更多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問過久遠，\N不過她說並不是有意這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:07:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…還是不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著聽著就會悲傷起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不協調…對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不協調的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您檢查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個真不錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給誰的禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了，謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好，也讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀先生，這位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友，要同樣款式的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個，十，百，千，萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來後，睡過一會兒了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被切斷的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法吹及的風
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能嚙合的齒輪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼地方不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin也說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我讓他聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也說過同樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin和久遠很相似…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁沒問題吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣沒關係嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這是她的意願，也就是說他選擇了直接面對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，讓你陪我買送給侄女的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面我是不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼著急吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開船還有一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亙理先生今天…那個…MU…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MU大戰死者聯合悼念大會準備會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開悼念會是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，在這之前不是還有另一件事應該處理好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對突然襲來的MU首先發動攻擊的是當時的駐日美軍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個原因，現在的美國已經沒有往日的威風了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是悲慘啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞說是美軍獨斷專行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上真正的操縱者另有其人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是當時國防部的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙讓部下承擔責任後就行蹤不明瞭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被誣陷的人是個好心腸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，據說是個很有前途的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事還有下文
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:12:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對MU使用戰術核武器的人是這個部下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他本人也不知道那是核彈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的，這個國家應該沒有核彈的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，就因為這樣，城市卻被完全摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼感想？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在猶豫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，那裡還有來不及逃走的平民
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心，這是對敵人的精確打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是軍人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是軍人的話，就要絕對服從上司的命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀先生應該也在國防部服過役吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2013年辭職的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想問你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼不做重新整編後的統合自衛隊的司令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是做了TERRA的司令呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為待遇上的差別嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能給我的侄女買這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好工作嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我工作的地方，倒是可以幫你介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在TERRA？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，地球聯合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你狠狠地將了一軍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，我不陪你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請請，浪費了你這麼多時間，不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是想贖罪嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是戰爭傻瓜啊，是不是，松鼠先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，怎麼硬塞給我們這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~兩位，工作結束了在約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，打擾了你們了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別開玩笑，只是收了如月博士的花，所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花？樹給的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，所以我想去買花瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是幫忙拿東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂指！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是兩個女人一起去吃燒肉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾爾菲今天好像沒喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人·神名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎？功刀司令的名字叫仁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然嗎，說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為，今天司令難得請假
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家多多少少都在談論這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:15:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠，今天對司令來說是特別的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挺有兩下子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在東京時我可是經常玩這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那以後的四個月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對RahXephon的操縱已經比較自如了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，你不是軍人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲結束，遊戲結束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你打算駕駛它到什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，忘記買花瓶了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了…沒關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看船嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇，真豪華！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是環島航行的水上餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在非常流行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲，兩位，在約會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過了不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…為什麼你會在這種地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管這個，說起約會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別的一天，是指約會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也不錯，約會的對象是她的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀先生已經結婚了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是女兒的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的Mouton-Rothschild
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:58.35,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mouton-Rothschild：一種法國葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:16:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道這種酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你不想知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經吃過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會接受邀請你是不是很吃驚？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看過錄像帶了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感想呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子很有前途
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很高的天賦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的罪過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以工作為借口不和她見面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你說得一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我接受你的邀請，\N因為我就要離開日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字也要改了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有放進上次的信裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這最後一段
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終還是決定把它交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是那孩子一邊\N想念著你一邊譜寫的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…感覺能讀懂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…因為我是個不求甚解的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀先生，剛剛有人送來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女孩子見面時應該準備鮮花 司令官\N——小嘍囉代表+1敬上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能給我看看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是給你的花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道司令和女兒約會成功了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺我們是在多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊！女孩子的心情只有我這個女孩子懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之父母與孩子之間的事，\N外人是不會明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，煩死了煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去做飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子餓了！
